title: Ralph Snart Adventures v1-v6 + Ex (1986-2008|DCP+)
description:
For more information on this series, please see the wikilink here: <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ralph_Snart_Adventures" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ralph_Snart_Adventures</a>

Some info from the official Ralph Snart fansite:
"Here it is, fatheads.......
Created, written and drawn by Marc Hansen, Ralph Snart Adventures was published from 1986-1993 by now defunct NOW Comics, and was the longest running comic in the entire NOW catalog, selling an average of 50,000 copies a month during that nine year period. Over 1 million comics were published!"

This is a funny and absurdist take on comics, and has some great art with hilarious dialogue. Definitely worth checking out of you like humorous stuff.

The torrent contains everything I could find, which appears to be mostly the complete v1-v6 and The Lost Issues, excluding issues 02 and 07 of the third volume. Everything is in a folder and labeled with dates as follows:

-The Lost Issues 01-03 (1993)
-v1 01 (1986)
-v2 01-08 (1986-1987)
-v3 01-26 (minus 02 and 07)  (1988-1990)
-v4 01-03 (1992)
-v5 01-04 (1993)
-v6 01 (2008)

All issues are DCP editions scanned by either Hartigan or GrumpyBear-DCP except v6 01, which is by TokerTheKid. Much thanks to all the scanners for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
